'''Bron''' was a [[God/Legends|god]] in a polytheistic religion followed by [[Purdy M. Trico]]. Other deities included [[Pula]] and [[Mugg]], and the religion's practices included wearing an amulet for good luck.<ref name="Dark Forces: Jedi Knight">[[Dark Forces: Jedi Knight]]</ref>

